  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/b5c964f14eb2ea07c56cc884b43a7f8f.poster.avif?t=1748014685\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/b5c964f14eb2ea07c56cc884b43a7f8f.webm?t=1748014685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/b5c964f14eb2ea07c56cc884b43a7f8f.mp4?t=1748014685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Ruin Hunters is a deckbuilding game with autobattler elements, where players must lead a party of three heroes. Wander into the deep of the dungeons, defeat enemies, gather treasures, while your party grows in power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ Turn-based combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ Use the environment (use it for cover, attack, or just simple push the enemy to it)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ Deck building (build your combat skill collections the way you would like to play)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/33c66ba9a60a800b2f263ee9567f03fd.poster.avif?t=1748014685\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/33c66ba9a60a800b2f263ee9567f03fd.webm?t=1748014685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/33c66ba9a60a800b2f263ee9567f03fd.mp4?t=1748014685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/b5c964f14eb2ea07c56cc884b43a7f8f.poster.avif?t=1748014685\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/b5c964f14eb2ea07c56cc884b43a7f8f.webm?t=1748014685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/b5c964f14eb2ea07c56cc884b43a7f8f.mp4?t=1748014685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Ruin Hunters is a deckbuilding game with autobattler elements, where players must lead a party of three heroes. Wander into the deep of the dungeons, defeat enemies, gather treasures, while your party grows in power.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Features:</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ Turn-based combat</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ Use the environment (use it for cover, attack, or just simple push the enemy to it)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >▪ Deck building (build your combat skill collections the way you would like to play)</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/33c66ba9a60a800b2f263ee9567f03fd.poster.avif?t=1748014685\" width=616 height=260 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/33c66ba9a60a800b2f263ee9567f03fd.webm?t=1748014685\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1211720/extras/33c66ba9a60a800b2f263ee9567f03fd.mp4?t=1748014685\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
